{"about_the_game":"Everything rides on your choices in this new wave interactive movie game. Experience a thrilling science fiction mystery in full-length live-action format\u2014from genius creator of the Danganronpa series, Kazutaka Kodaka!<br><br>Simple, intuitive controls mean playing Death Come True is as easy as watching a movie!<br><br>The choices you make propel the story forward. Which ending awaits?<br><br><strong>Introduction</strong><br>You wake up in a hotel room, roused by the shrill ring of the bedside phone.<br>You take the call. It's the hotel concierge.<br>&quot;If you have any issues, please feel free to visit the front desk.&quot;<br>You have absolutely no idea how you ended up here.<br>Disoriented, you try to take stock of your surroundings when you stumble across a woman, tied up and unconscious.<br>Still reeling from the shock, you notice the story on the evening news: You. A wanted serial killer.<br>Then comes a persistent knocking on the door...<br><br><strong>Cast</strong><br>Kanata Hongo as Makoto Karaki<br>Chiaki Kuriyama as Akane Sachimura<br>Win Morisaki as Nozomu Kuji<br>Yuki Kaji as the Concierge<br>Chihiro Yamamoto as Nene Kurushima<br>Jiro Sato as Kenichi Mino<br><br><strong>Theme Song</strong><br>Inner Circle<br>Kami-sama, I have noticed (Warner Music Japan)<br><br><strong>Death Medals</strong><br>Each gruesome death you experience comes with a reward in the form of &quot;Death Medals.&quot; Acquiring these medals in turn unlocks bonus &quot;DeathTube&quot; clips. Try and collect them all!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shot by the Police","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1321070/832d1324e159d919c4a785c8a0ddae124954fd4d.jpg"},{"name":"Bludgeoned by a Steel Pipe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1321070/adce6a3210076180055c4b6c966509834ccf7c64.jpg"},{"name":"Stabbed by a Katana","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/